{"tid":1479827,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人道主義慈善機構捐款","createTime":"2019-08-17T05:07:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T12:49:23.000Z","uid":301633,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aa437f0e8054f86b00021b533cfad52508a46d13","tid":1479827,"uid":301633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:07:38.000Z","msg":"有2個問題我想了良久都想唔明。<br />\n1)宗教團體一向不大參與政治能理解，但人道立場支援一向會提供，例如有些聖堂開放會所招待避險的年輕人。但大慈大悲的佛教組織連超道法會都好似無聽見。<br />\n<br />\n2)那些一向以人道為本的xx會一大堆，對香港出現的不人道現象零聲音。戶之全世界人民都聲援香港。<br />\n我捐助這些機構最耐的有30年，想來想去唔明白，所以今天我去信所有我長期資助的慈善機構停止資助，表明我對此不滿，且會將所慳回的金錢用於直接支援香港。"},{"pid":"e7551bcaaba375f70bf3e3b1ca0b07e77a0fc75a","tid":1479827,"uid":301633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:12:16.000Z","msg":"大家比D意見"},{"pid":"ac281e6579373ac4cec793cb3fcc459bf1241c6f","tid":1479827,"uid":17812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:49:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R6z7q5Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR6z7q5Y.jpg&h=cc2f3dc6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MpTzQxD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMpTzQxD.jpg&h=8a83645e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SD7g3SE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSD7g3SE.jpg&h=c3d87592&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pMxkL50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpMxkL50.jpg&h=712e21f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NGNMGEk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNGNMGEk.jpg&h=be0e5720&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zDmBjq1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzDmBjq1.jpg&h=4071fb3f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nvdj1Em.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnvdj1Em.jpg&h=c91c4e